com.i2group.apollo.model.schema

Interface IGeospatialSourceData


  • public interface IGeospatialSourceData
    A geospatial location represented in its source data form.
    Since:
    4.0

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      List<CompoundPropertyValue> getData()
      Gets CompoundPropertyValues containing source data that describes a geographical location.
      String getType()
      Gets a String describing the type of some source data that describes a geospatial location.

    • Method Detail

      • getType

        String getType()
        Gets a String describing the type of some source data that describes a geospatial location. The type information allows callers to parse the return value of getData() successfully.
        Returns:
        See above.

      • getData

        List<CompoundPropertyValue> getData()
        Gets CompoundPropertyValues containing source data that describes a geographical location. The structure of this information is determined by the return value of getType().
        Returns:
        See above.
